sp.p:
3. Papists Ordination enters them into a false Church in
Specie (a pretended catholick Church headed by the Pope);
but our Pastors entered them into no Church but Christs.

                  What, when I have covenanted Assent and Consent to all
things in their Book, and subscribed to use no other form in baptizing;
and also must be cast out for it?

3. If I do it not, I am guilty of it if I declare my Consent to
Accuse all such within fourteen days, that the Ordinary may do it;
and to Covenant and Swear Canonical Obedience to him.

If there be any Sentences out of it there inserted, those are part;
else the Apocrypha is no part of the Book: It is only the Order to
read it that is a part.

But you know that if there must three Consents go to it;
The Ordainers, the Patrons, and the Communicants, they may
never agree▪ and frustrate all.
